3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with the robustness of large networked systems, such as transportation and communication networks, which is a topic of interest in networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the resilience of large systems, which is a topic of interest in systems and control.
